name: The Queen's Dreams: Nirvana
description:
In the beginning there was Nirvana. A peaceful Savannah with green, blue and gold as far as the eye could see.
Each animal, one by one, grazed and groomed. 
Slow pace.
Fresh breeze.
Flowers of every kind.
The commencement of a crowned beginning. A pasture new.
She was born. 
A natural garden of beauty shall be her dwelling on Earth.
